    "description": "Join the SpiceJet Cargo family as a Warehouse Manager in Raipur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout SpiceJet Cargo:\nSpiceJet Cargo is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SpiceJet Cargo!",
